592. FROM JOHN F1snmz.

Deventer MS. 91, f. 101. Rochester. LB. App. 428. (c. June 1517).

[Evidently written in response to the first news of Erasmus’ journey back to the Continent, and therefore to a letter contemporary with Ep. 584. As that is answered by Ep. 601, which was accompanied also by the letters from the Venetians asked for in Ep. 584, this letter may be taken as that mentioned in Ep. 601 ; and may therefore be dated in June or July.]
